high_descs: move to the shelf behind you
pick up a sponge from the sponge
move to the sink behind you
clean the sponge on the sink
move to the shelf to the right of you
put the sponge on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around, towards to white shelf.
Pick up the green and yellow sponge on the left of the first shelf.
Turn back around and go to the sink on your right.
Place the sponge inside the sink, turn the water on and clean the sink, turn the water off, and remove the sponge from the sink.
Turn to your right and go back to the white shelf, on the wall, across the room.
Place the sponge on the bottom white shelf, hanging from the wall.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on the shelf.

high_descs: wet the sponge in the sink
drop the sponge on the shelf
anns.task_desc: drop a wet sponge on the shelf
